@host = http://127.0.0.1:5055

### Root status
GET {{host}}/
Accept: application/json

### Convert sample.jpg from the app working directory
GET {{host}}/sample

### Upload a file and convert it to PNG
POST {{host}}/convert
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=magiccrash-boundary

--magiccrash-boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample.jpg
--magiccrash-boundary--